The paper discusses the use of word embeddings in natural language processing and ontology population, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and database systems (cs.DB) as it deals with maintaining concept hierarchies in a selected domain.
